name: TriathlonChecklist
0:
”Alexa, open Triathlon Checklist”
”Alexa, ask Triathlon Checklist for triathlon”
”Alexa, ask Triathlon Checklist for cycling”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: triathlon checklist
des:
Triathlon checklist makes it easier to remember all gear needed for a triathlon race day. You can go through entire tri checklist or pick just one of the following categories: swim, bike, run, food, other.
Skill also enables to re-read other categories before quitting.
